The problem: `tsc` only compiles `.ts` files, so `src/hooks/*.sh` never lands in `dist/hooks/`. The `copyHooks()` function silently skips missing files. And for Bun compile (standalone binary), filesystem-based hook resolution won't work at all.

The fix: embed hook scripts as string constants in TypeScript (works everywhere), add a `postbuild` script to also copy `.sh` files to `dist/hooks/`, and add warnings when hooks aren't found.
